Uchi Technologies Bhd.

                    Uchi Technologies Bhd. is an investment holding company, which engages in the provision of management services. The company is principally involved in original design manufacturing, specializing in the design of electronic control systems. It operates through the following segments: Investment Holding, Manufacturing, and Trading. The Investment Holding segment includes management services. The Manufacturing segment is the manufacture of touch screen advance display, light measurement equipments, mixed signal control system and laboratory equipment, mixed signal microprocessor based application, system integration products and electronics modules. The Trading segment refers to the trade of complete electric module and saturated paper for PCB lamination. The company was founded on February 18, 1998 and is headquartered in Prai, Malaysia.                  




